---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Memorandum | Phantom">
	<main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 min-h-screen">
        <a href="/" class="text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary mb-12 block text-sm">&larr; system_root</a>
        
        <article class="prose prose-invert prose-green">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-primary tracking-tight">The Best Interface is No Interface.</h1>
            <div class="h-px w-20 bg-primary mb-10"></div>
            
            <p class="text-xl text-foreground leading-relaxed mb-8">
                Product Managers spend 40% of their time acting as human routers. Copying data from Linear to Slack. Summarizing Zoom calls into Notion. Updating stakeholders who could have just checked the dashboard.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground mb-8">
                We built Phantom to kill that job.
            </p>
            
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-white">The Invisible OS</h2>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6">
                Phantom is not a destination. It doesn't want you to log in. It doesn't want your eyeballs.
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6">
                It lives in the accessibility tree of your browser. It tailing your logs in Terminal. It's a ghost in your Slack channels.
            </p>
            
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-muted-foreground mb-10">
                <li><strong class="text-white">Channel Native:</strong> We meet you where you work.</li>
                <li><strong class="text-white">Lane-Based Execution:</strong> Predictable, serial task queues. No async chaos.</li>
                <li><strong class="text-white">Zero Decay Memory:</strong> A markdown-based second brain that never forgets context.</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="bg-muted/30 border border-muted p-6 rounded-lg my-12">
                <code class="text-sm text-green-400">
                    > "Phantom is not a tool you use.<br/>
                    > It is a member of your team."
                </code>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-muted flex justify-between items-center">
                <span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">End of Transmission.</span>
                <a href="/protocols" class="bg-primary text-black px-6 py-2 rounded font-bold hover:bg-green-400 transition-colors">
                    Read Protocols
                </a>
            </div>
        </article>
	</main>
</Layout>
